<s> Hi Fernando, Did you try -latin1 to specify you have extended chars?  </s>
<s> If the characters are Latin1 (ISO-8859-1) symbols, then Tidy should read the raw characters and emit nice HTML entities (either numeric or symbolic).  </s>
<s> If your symbol characters are in some other encoding (Windows-1252?  </s>
<s> Mac Roman?), you may still be able to get Tidy to recognize them.  </s>
<s> See http://tidy.sf.net/docs/quickref.html#char-encoding  </s>
<s> If that doesn't work, send us a small sample.  </s>
